{"tid":2139443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正名亞博社區治療設施為謝婉雯醫院","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T03:45:48.000Z","uid":266788,"like":48,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4ab11b3b4e580dce6835e012818d3d72077a7a","tid":2139443,"uid":266788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"亞博個臨時醫院完工啦，多謝醫護。<br />\n<br />\n英國因為肺炎起左好幾個臨時醫院，並以現代護理學奠基者南丁格爾命名NHS Nightingale Hospital。<br />\n<br />\n英國有南丁格爾，我地香港同樣有無私醫護入dirty team，03沙士更有幾位醫護為香港殉職，當中謝婉雯醫生更被譽為&ldquo;香港女兒&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n我建議香港政府應以同樣行動肯定香港醫者多年為香港既貢獻及紀念沙士殉職醫者。與其叫唔知咩咩醫院，倒不如正名亞博臨時醫院為&ldquo;<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">謝婉雯紀念醫院</span></strong>&rdquo;，齊心抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6izJrJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6izJrJY.jpg&h=863f7743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(source:BBC)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E8%8C%83%E9%B4%BB%E9%BD%A1%E5%90%8C%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E9%A6%AC%E4%BB%B2%E5%84%80-%E8%A6%96%E4%B9%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%A5%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E8%258C%2583%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E9%25BD%25A1%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2587%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E5%2584%2580-%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25B9%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=443448f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandne